title: MS Build version update causing dependency conflict

nodes.body: It was fixed by a different team: https://dev.azure.com/onebranch/Support/_workitems/edit/198755

I've checked with the people from the work chat I'm involved in and they are unsure why the ticket was closed. So this one is still ongoing.
At least I got some new information after asking them.

We've got an internal chat and internal ticket for this one.
Currently we're blocked and waiting for additional data from the customer if they choose to cooperate.
If that happens I will reopen this ticket, until then I'm closing it.
